26
00:01:13,583 --> 00:01:16,042
when the guy said it'd take a week to make.

27
00:01:16,042 --> 00:01:17,667
Oh.

28
00:01:17,667 --> 00:01:20,792
Maybe it's a lost cause after all...

29
00:01:20,792 --> 00:01:22,958
No.

30
00:01:22,958 --> 00:01:25,875
There's still another way.

31
00:01:25,875 --> 00:01:28,958
If I wait for the time leap
machine to be finished tomorrow

32
00:01:28,958 --> 00:01:31,042
and then go back in time...

33
